videos.headline: Utah State's Repp brings in nasty 1-handed TD
videos.description: Utah State tight end Caleb Repp snags the ball with his left hand over the Boise State defender for the Aggies touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Utah State’s Repp brings in nasty 1-handed TD) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hightower takes shovel pass 30 yards for TD
videos.description: Jaylon Henderson tosses the football to John Hightower who flies down the sideline for a 30-yard Boise State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Hightower takes shovel pass 30 yards for TD) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Boise State runs statue of liberty for TD
videos.description: Jaylon Henderson fakes a throw then hands it off behind his back to George Holani for the statue of liberty touchdown.
